title: #372 - Eddie Bravo
description:
Eddie Bravo, Owner of 10th Planet Jiu Jitsu , joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.
 
The Sixth Eddie Bravo Invitational takes place April 24, 2016 at the Orpheum Theatre in Los Angeles, CA and being streamed live for the first time on UFC Fight Pass.
 
All info can be found here: http://www.eddiebravoinvitational.com/
